task.summary: This small universe is created for doing small sketches about chemical-physical experiments. It has a single important rule, the particles (Tha RandomWalker) move depending of probabilities.
Goal: World created as a unique class. Any other class it is not required. So, I need to implement a few methods to do the interfacing. I just did a couple of them.
Iterations implemented... now we will change the collision handling process
Iterations moved to a independent class!!! Developing Shape!!!
